nodes.title: OriginalImagePrompt
widgets_values: a stormy sea scene. The composition centers on a large, old-fashioned sailing ship battling turbulent waves, with its sails tattered and partially illuminated by the fiery glow of a lighthouse in the background. The lighthouse stands tall on a rocky outcrop, its light piercing through the dark, swirling storm clouds. The color palette is dominated by deep blues and grays, contrasted by the warm yellows and oranges of the lighthouse's light, creating a striking visual contrast. The waves are depicted with dynamic brushstrokes, emphasizing the chaos and power of the ocean. The overall mood is intense and foreboding, capturing the perilous nature of the sea during a storm.
